---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Upkeepy — Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Effective: March 4, 2026</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Upkeepy does not collect, store, or share any personal data. Period.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">All your maintenance tasks, completion history, and preferences are stored locally on your device. If you enable iCloud sync, your data is synced privately through your personal iCloud account — we never see it, access it, or store it on our servers.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">What We Don't Collect</h2>
    <ul class="text-gray-300 mb-4 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
      <li>No personal information (name, email, address)</li>
      <li>No usage analytics or tracking</li>
      <li>No advertising identifiers</li>
      <li>No location data</li>
      <li>No third-party SDKs or analytics tools</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">No Account Required</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Upkeepy does not require you to create an account, sign in, or provide any personal information to use the app.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">In-App Purchases</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Purchases are processed entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not receive or store any payment information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Push Notifications</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Upkeepy uses local push notifications to remind you about upcoming maintenance tasks. These are scheduled entirely on your device — no external servers involved.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Upkeepy does not collect any data from any user, including children under 13.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Changes</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">If we ever change this policy, we'll update this page. But our policy is "we don't collect your data" and that's not changing.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">justinbundrick@gmail.com</a></p>

    <p class="mt-12 text-gray-500 text-sm">© 2026 Justin Bundrick</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
